<p></p>
<h3><b>The journey</b></h3>
<p>Transitions from house to ceremony to reception all allow for candid, on-the-go photos. Don’t put your camera away during the walk or drive—some of the best wedding photos are taken when you’re on the way from one place to another.</p>
<div class="pixels-photo">
<p><img src="https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/111606181/m%3D900/v2?sig=4ad7a797b35e5767e621ad7af0138cf247ab107a1922a5a37a985d6dac8cd152" alt="A man with a girl and a guitar has the world. by Photocillin Photography on 500px.com"></p>
