<p> </p>
</div>
<p></p>
<h3><b>The entertainment</b></h3>
<p>Whether they chose a live band or a DJ, the couple will want to remember the music.</p>
<div class="pixels-photo">
<p><img src="https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/128825767/m%3D900/v2?sig=281b1cc806f75e69db2bc9ccc5a6cb6eebbfb4f0219337b87e4614e83ad73ac2" alt="The DJ by Gerrit Phil Baumann on 500px.com"></p>
