<p>500px featured a gallery called 30 Days of Weddings, highlighting individual photographers in the 500px Community who take amazing wedding photography shots year after year. Make sure to follow these accounts for inspiration.</p>
<div class="pixels-photo">
<p><img src="https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/280928107/m%3D900/v2?sig=bc4b0b14b3ecf5217ba4fbb5be8b7a806c78d0e29bfb516b14ff7b799069b6c7" alt="Wedding photography - L''attente by Cédric Nicolle on 500px.com"></p>
