<p>Carey Nash‘s wedding and engagement portraits ooze drama and grandeur—and we are suckers for drama and grandeur. From far away helicopter shots of the bride and groom running across an epic landscape, to a ‘trash the dress’ silhouette among swirling dust in Cabo, Carey gets the highest compliment we can pay a wedding photographer.</p>
<div class="pixels-photo">
<p><img src="https://drscdn.500px.org/photo/112817499/m%3D900/v2?sig=1cc819248162378fd85efa5d8081f0094e91724f67c66858733bbde657c85899" alt="Wedding photography - Mountain Bride by Carey Nash on 500px.com"></p>
