<p><strong>Malibu theme</strong></p>
<p><img src="https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CaliforniaDreaming-ByBettinaBogar-8.jpg" alt="photo shoot - CaliforniaDreaming-ByBettinaBogar-8" width="3840" height="5760" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-34860" srcset="https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CaliforniaDreaming-ByBettinaBogar-8.jpg 3840w, https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CaliforniaDreaming-ByBettinaBogar-8-333x500.jpg 333w, https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CaliforniaDreaming-ByBettinaBogar-8-768x1152.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 3840px) 100vw, 3840px"></p>
<p><img src="https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CaliforniaDreaming-ByBettinaBogar-10.jpg" alt="photo shoot - CaliforniaDreaming-ByBettinaBogar-10" width="5760" height="3840" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-34861" srcset="https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CaliforniaDreaming-ByBettinaBogar-10.jpg 5760w, https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CaliforniaDreaming-ByBettinaBogar-10-1500x1000.jpg 1500w, https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CaliforniaDreaming-ByBettinaBogar-10-500x333.jpg 500w, https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CaliforniaDreaming-ByBettinaBogar-10-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 5760px) 100vw, 5760px"></p>
<p><strong>Western theme</strong></p>
<p><img src="https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/bettinabogar_westernwonders_005.jpg" alt="photo shoot - bettinabogar_westernwonders_005" width="2404" height="1800" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-34858" srcset="https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/bettinabogar_westernwonders_005.jpg 2404w, https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/bettinabogar_westernwonders_005-500x374.jpg 500w, https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/bettinabogar_westernwonders_005-768x575.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 2404px) 100vw, 2404px"></p>
<p><img src="https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/bettinabogar_westernwonders_008.jpg" alt="photo shoot - bettinabogar_westernwonders_008" width="5509" height="3673" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-34859" srcset="https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/bettinabogar_westernwonders_008.jpg 5509w, https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/bettinabogar_westernwonders_008-1500x1000.jpg 1500w, https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/bettinabogar_westernwonders_008-500x333.jpg 500w, https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/bettinabogar_westernwonders_008-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 5509px) 100vw, 5509px"></p>
<p><strong>Joshua Tree theme</strong></p>
